Aim:create twin coloured chemical test.
Apparatus:warm water,green water colour,lemon drops,baking soda,eno,mustard oil and a transparent container.
Procedure:
(i)pour half level of warm water in the container,add few amount of green water colour,then mixed it up well. when it got mixeed, add few drops of lemon , 1 teaspoon of baking soda and 1 teaspoon of eno then mixed it very well.afer sometimes pour the mustard oil slowly after pouring it shake up the container afterthat twin colours will be noticed , this includes the colour of mustard oil and the colour of mixture .   
